},{"SurveyID":"SV_ey2E6mpIE7A0OuG","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID18","SecondaryAttribute":"Thank you for completing the survey. To enter the raffle, please provide a valid email address be...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Thank you for completing the survey. To enter the raffle, please provide a valid email address below.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q18","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"FORM","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Thank you for completing the survey. To enter the raffle, please provide a valid email address be...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Email Address","TextEntry":"on","TextEntryValidation":"ValidEmail"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":2,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionID":"QID18","DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"LogicType":"Question","QuestionID":"QID25","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID25\/SelectableChoice\/1","Operator":"Selected","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID25","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID25\/SelectableChoice\/1","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Are you interested in the raffle?<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Yes!<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Selected<\/span> "},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_ey2E6mpIE7A0OuG","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID19","SecondaryAttribute":"Informed Consent Agreement for Participation in a Research Study \u00a0 Investigators:\u00a0 Kyle Smith, We.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h3><strong>Informed Consent Agreement for Participation in a Research Study <\/strong><\/h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n<h3><strong>Investigators:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n<p>Kyle Smith, Weaver Goldman, Ryan Pote<br>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<h3><strong>Contact Information:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n<p>gr-windhoek-26-teamgraduate@wpi.edu<br>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<h3><strong>Title of Research Study:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n<p>Empowering #TeamGraduate Educators: Generative AI Tools for Secondary E-Learning in Namibia<br>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<h3><strong>Sponsor:<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n<p>#TeamGraduate<br>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<h4><u><strong>Introduction<\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\nYou are being asked to participate in a research study. Before you agree, however, you must be fully informed about the purpose of the study, the procedures to be followed, and any benefits, risks, or discomfort that you may experience as a result of your participation. This form presents information about the study so that you may make a fully informed decision regarding your participation.\n\n<h4><br>\n<u><strong>Purpose<\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\nThe purpose of this study is to compile a set of user interface (UI) design characteristics that are engaging and locally relevant. Additionally, this study aims to identify key features that drive the use of online academic resources.\n\n<h4><br>\n<u><strong>Procedures to be Followed <\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\n\n<p>The following survey is divided into two sections: UI design choices and features of online academic resources.<br>\n<br>\nIn the first section, participants will be asked to choose between two UI design options, selecting the one that is most appealing and easy to understand. After making a selection, participants will have the option to briefly explain their choice, noting the key features that led them to their decision. Please note that the explanation is optional and not required for the survey; it is simply present to collect additional data.<br>\n<br>\nThe second section will ask participants to rank the effectiveness of a given feature on a scale of 1-5 stars. If a feature is rated 1 or 5 stars, participants can optionally explain their choice. Lastly, participants will be able to answer an open-ended question about other e-learning resources.<\/p><p><\/p><p><\/p><p><br><\/p><p>\n\nThis survey should take no more than 10 minutes to complete.<\/p>\n\n<h4><br>\n<u><strong>Risks to Study Participants<\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\n\n<p>There are no foreseeable risks or discomfort that participants should experience.<\/p>\n\n<h4><br>\n<u><strong>Benefits to Research Participants and Others<\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\n\n<p>The results of this survey will be used to improve the #TeamGraduate online learning platform and provide additional educational resources to Namibian students.<\/p>\n\n<h4><br>\n<u><strong>Record Keeping and Confidentiality:<\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\n\n<p>All data collected during this project will be kept confidential in a Private Google Drive, accessible only to the members of the IQP project, project advisors, and team sponsor: Helena Mboti. Additionally, participants will remain anonymous in the results of our project. Emails will only be collected if participants choose to enter a raffle.<\/p>\n\n<h4><br>\n<u><strong>Contact Information <\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\n\n<p>For more information about this research or about the rights of research participants, or in the case of research-related injury, please contact: gr-windhoek-26-teamgraduate@wpi.edu<\/p>\n\n<p><u>Additional Contacts:<\/u><\/p>\n\n<p>IRB Manager: Ruth McKeogh - (508) 831- 6699 - irb@wpi.edu<br>\nHuman Protection Administrator - Gabriel Johnson - (508) 831-4989 - gjohnson@wpi.edu<\/p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<h4><u><strong>Your Participation in this Research is Voluntary<\/strong><\/u><\/h4>\n\n<p>Your refusal to participate will not result in any penalty to you or any loss of benefits to which you may otherwise be entitled. You may decide to stop participating in the research at any time without penalty or loss of other benefits. The project investigators retain the right to cancel or postpone the experimental procedures at any time they see fit.<\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q19","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Informed Consent Agreement for Participation in a Research Study \u00a0 Investigators:\u00a0 Kyle Smith, We...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID19"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_ey2E6mpIE7A0OuG","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID2","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DataExportTag":"Q2","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Click to write the question text","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Click to write Choice 1"},"2":{"Display":"Click to write Choice 2"},"3":{"Display":"Click to write Choice 3"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID2"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_ey2E6mpIE7A0OuG","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID20","SecondaryAttribute":"E-learning UI and Feature Survey\u00a0 Monetary Compensation Participants will have the option to prov..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h2><strong>E-learning UI and Feature Survey&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2><div><strong><br><\/strong><\/div>\n\n<h3><u><strong>Monetary Compensation<\/strong><\/u><\/h3>\n\n<p>Participants will have the option to provide a valid email address to enter a raffle. Two <b>N$400<\/b> prizes will be awarded to randomly selected participants. Emails will only be collected on completion of the survey. Winners will be contacted via email after the survey is concluded.<\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q20","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Privat